            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Imperante domno nostro <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/110">Lodohvvico</persName> magno <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperatore</rs>, anno imperi sui undecimo, die
                        tercio, indicione nona. Per anc pagina livelli do adque trado ego <persName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Abbots" ref="#people/1237"
                            >Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> de <rs key="#Monasteries">monesterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Wood #Coloni/tenants #Rent_in_kind #Exenia #Operae #Actionarii/actores #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Monasteries #Abbots"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/47"><placeName ref="#places/15"
                                >Nonantolas</placeName></orgName> vobis <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants"><name ref="Gisbertus">Gixeberto</name></persName>
                        filio quondam <persName><name ref="Sigebertus"
                        >Sichgeverto</name></persName>, seo et alio <persName key="#Coloni/tenants"
                                ><name ref="Gisbertus">Gixeberto</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Sigebertus">Sigeverto</name></persName> liberis
                        ominibus. Idest <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">sortem</rs> ilia qui
                        est positas in <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Coloni/tenants #Rent_in_kind #Minores #Operae #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Wine #Legumes #Maiores #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Wood #Hay/fodder#Fruits/vegetables #Houses"
                            ref="#places/2492">Ostilia</placeName>, in tantum in quantum ante os
                        dies per <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Dominicus"
                                >Dominico</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">masario</rs> nostro rectam fuit, qui
                        pertenit da parte ipsius monesterio tam sedimen cum <rs key="#Houses"
                            >casa</rs>, curtem, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">orteo</rs>, areis, tam
                        teris, arvis et vineis, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pradis</rs>, pascui, <rs
                            key="#Wood">silvi</rs>, salectis, adiciis, vel <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">usum aquarum</rs> in
                        integrum. Ipsis rebus do vobis vel ad vestris heredis ad lavorandum et super
                        resedere et lavorare et meliorare debeatis sine fraude vel nelicto,
                        livellario nomine, usque ad annis nomero viginti et nove. <rs
                            key="#Rent_in_kind">Et reditum</rs> exinde persolvere repromitimus nos
                            <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">colonis</rs> et nostris heredis de ipsis rebus
                        ad parte ipsius monesterio aut miso eius quid supervenerit de omnium laborem
                        quem ibidem Dominus laborantibus dederit: de <rs key="#Maiores">maiorimen
                            cova</rs> quarta in campo, <rs key="#Legumes">legumen</rs> modio quarto
                        in area, <rs key="#Minores">menudo</rs> modio quinto in area, lino magna
                        quarta, <rs key="#Wine">vinum</rs> quarto. <rs key="#Exenia">Esenio</rs>
                        vero per omni anno dinarios quatuordicem et ipso esenio datum et conpletum
                        sit in misa sancti Martini. <rs key="#Operae">Operas</rs> vero per omni anno
                        manibiles die sex et ipsas operas facere debeat in Ostilia cum annona
                        domnica per tempore mesis vel vindimias <rs key="#Actionarii/actores">miso
                            domnico</rs> cum onore sussipiendum et sucepta facere promitimus; sic
                        tamen ipso censum vel reditum nos colonis vel nostris heredis cum nostro
                        dispendio vegere debeat ad <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cella</rs> vostra in
                            <placeName
                            key="#Rent_in_kind #Minores #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Wine #Legumes #Maiores #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#places/1538"><geogName
                                key="#Rent_in_kind #Minores #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Wine #Legumes #Maiores #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#estates/1111">Piscaria</geogName></placeName> et consignare
                        repromitimus ad miso domnico nam alio nullam. Ego patrono vel mei sucepsores
                        vobis suprascriptis colonis vel ad vestris heredis nullam superinponere
                        debeamus nisi qualiter superiuscriptum est. Pena vero inter nobis stetit qui
                        non conpleverit vel permanserit in eo homnia qualiter superius legitur, et
                        certe aparuerit veritas, tunc conponat pars partis ubi culpa respeserit ad
                        illa parte qui in sua fidem permanserit pena nomine solidos viginti et nove,
                        pos pena soluta pagina in sua maneat firmitatem. Duos livellos uno tinore
                        scriptis ad omnia suprascripta. Acto Ostilia, feliciter.  Et de orto et de
                        rapas et fasioli unde non redatis. + Petrus abbas manu mea subscripsi.
                        Signum (S) manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Bertus"
                            >Bertoni</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Ursus"
                                >Ursoni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Witness">testis</rs>. Signum (S) manus <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Ursus">Ursoni</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petroni</name></persName> testis.
                        Signum (S) manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Romanus"
                            >Romano</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Venerus"
                                >Venerio</name></persName> testis.   </ab>
                </div>
